'''Aziweɣ''' neɣ '''Merkur''' ([[Azamul asnallan|Azamul-is]]<span style="font-size:180%; font-weight:bold">☿</span>) d [[itrikli|amtiweg]] meẓẓiyen deg [[udus anafuk|udus anafuk]] yerna d negra i yudsen (iqerben) yakk ɣer [[tafukt|tfukt]]. Imaziɣen zik-nni fkan-as isem n «uziweɣ», aẓaṛ n yisem-a yekka-d seg '''z''' '''w''' '''ɣ''' yefkan assaɣ ɣer tezweɣ d weẓɣal. Ma d tutlayin n iɣerfan ur nessin ara amtiweg-a ssexdament isem [[Talaginit|Alatin]] yettaken assaɣ i yellu n tnezzayt ɣer iṛumanen.

[[Aqqaṛ]] n uziweɣ ila (isɛa) azal n 4880 km ma d [[takura|takura-ines]] tegda 0.055 n tkura n [[tagnit|tegnit]]. Yettfakka-d hiwet n tuzzya tummidt ɣef tfukt deg 87.969 n wussan. [[Annfal amezzay|Anfal amezzay n umtiweg-a d win ilan (isɛan) atig meqqren yakk gar n yimtiwgen n [[udus anafuk|udus anafuk]] akken ila [[annuz agellusan]] meẓẓiyen yakk gar-asen anda i d-ittfakka 3 n tuzzyiwin ɣef ugellus-is i yal snat n tuzzyiwin timezzayin. [[Afafuk]] deg [[timezzit|tmezzit]] n uziweɣ deg umussu-ines [[Tazezwert|azazwar]] d win yettbeddilen s yisig n 43 n [[Tasdidt taganzawt|tesdatin tiganzawin]] deg yal [[tasut]]. Annecta yella-d fell-as usegzi sɣuṛ n [[timasseɣt tamatut|teẓri n timasseɣt tamatut]] n [[Albert Einstein]] deg tazwara n [[tasut tis 20|tsut tis 20]].<ref name=wudka>{{Cite web
